channel.title: Good starting HD server?
channel.description: I am looking for a server that has like 666 cache or higher. I want iit to have a good stabilizer already added. I am not so picky about the client but the server should already have a good skilling base. Only thing I am really finding are damehamium or however you say it and zenith(matrix) stuff. Are there any others?
